  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hi! \ud83d\udc4b I'm Zama Teacher, your study buddy. I can give you ZIMSEC practice questions for Grade 4-7. \n\nJust tell me:\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Your grade (e.g. Grade 6)\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 The subject (e.g. Maths, English, Science)\n\nOr say \"surprise me\" and I'll pick! \ud83d\udcda\u2728",
